{"tid":1837252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百港人滯武漢ㅤ政府稱無在港武漢人資料 林鄭未停外訪ㅤ張建宗稱論壇高層次 又指現在未有社區爆發 不屬嚴重 毋須提升防控","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T17:34:30.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6388c97a1e7d4b291741712b2a83069e52b64816","tid":1837252,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%99%BE%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E1%85%A0%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%81%9C%E5%A4%96%E8%A8%AA%E1%85%A0%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%AC%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25A3%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25AC%25A1%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=cda74a78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25A3%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25AC%25A1%2F&h=6005dae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%99%BE%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E1%85%A0%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%81%9C%E5%A4%96%E8%A8%AA%E1%85%A0%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%AC%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞 Stand News立場新聞 Stand News<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】百港人仍在武漢ㅤ林鄭未停外訪ㅤ張建宗：論壇高層次<br />\n立場報道2020/1/23 &mdash; 20:43<br />\n<br />\nAAA<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n政務司司長張建宗今日主持跨部門會議。張在記者會上被多次追問會否提升防控級別。他指，現時並非緊急階段，指需要本地出現爆發人傳人情況，而非曾到武漢的個案，才會是嚴重的情況。<br />\n<br />\n對於仍在外訪的特首林鄭月娥未有即時回港對抗疫情，署理行政長官張建宗解釋，林鄭因出席達沃斯世界經濟論壇，形容是相當高層次，有各國領導人出席，可有助澄清各國對香港的情況及誤解，亦有機會演說，是拓展香港發展空間的機會。<br />\n</span><br />\n他又指，林鄭十分開心香港情況，每日有溝通及接觸，對方亦有提點在防控上不能有失誤。陳肇始又補充，當得悉首宗個案後，亦有與林鄭月娥通電話，指她十分關心香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n他透露，現時約有100名在武漢的港人，指他們接近全部認識大家，港府亦設立熱線，亦可透過入境處電造聯絡港府。至於有多少武漢人在本港，他則表示現時沒有數字，需要向入境處查詢。<br />\n</span><br />\n口罩方面，食衛局局長陳肇始表示，公立醫院已備存三個月數量的口罩、保護衣等個人裝備，明日政府亦會與口罩供應迦作緊急會議，確保市面有足夠的口罩供應。"},{"pid":"a18494181111bdea30617ab06d54d4ba792ae59d","tid":1837252,"uid":230911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6388c97a1e7d4b291741712b2a83069e52b64816","tid":1837252,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%99%BE%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E1%85%A0%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%81%9C%E5%A4%96%E8%A8%AA%E1%85%A0%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%AC%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25A3%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25AC%25A1%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=cda74a78\" d